{"tid":2290474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AESPA 官方粉絲名稱公開 我係MY呀吊！！！","createTime":"2020-11-18T04:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T06:20:59.000Z","uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"81c9c8e0c4cdb6bbdc35c55f9cffceef68a315b7","tid":2290474,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LaHqG1S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLaHqG1S.jpg&h=7ad1a18f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDFvS8y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDFvS8y.jpg&h=a84ec255&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GUQS6tB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGUQS6tB.jpg&h=80f765fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtO9pfh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtO9pfh.jpg&h=a6db5837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四位成員透過官方聲明稿傳達了出道的感想與未來的期許。<br />\n<br />\n首先，KARINA 表示：「還是不敢相信這是真的，雖然有壓力，但想盡全力向全世界展現好的歌曲與舞台。」，GISELLE 則感覺很新奇，有那麼多人對她們感興趣，所以會更加努力，讓大家看到她們進步的樣子。<br />\n<br />\nWINTER 表示：「很開心能向大家展現我到目前為止練習的表演，我的目標是成為能向大家展現明朗又積極形象的 aespa 與 WINTER 的。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，aespa 也透過 V LIVE 頻道與官方網站公開她們的粉絲名稱是「MY」(與英文單詞發音相同)，意思是「我珍貴的朋友」"},{"pid":"abeed2ab831d70d8dd2c85ed44b032c264c983e8","tid":2290474,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"樓主低級紅"},{"pid":"5ea24ca5256f1da0f873723f8a9f093b42c4f6d9","tid":2290474,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"冬天係ok靚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135bd1ce2c50ce4ec2bcbaac75c2518ed58567b0","tid":2290474,"uid":313222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:43:25